data.description: *AMAZING ONE OF A FEW CINDER-BLOCK BUILT HOMES IN THIS AREA* HERE IS YOUR CHANCE TO OWN THIS BEAUTY, 1.06 ACRES FULLY FENCED & GATED. Very nice remodeling has been performed. This Home is not large, yet very efficient and cozy. This Home Features (2) Rooms, (1) Full Bathroom, Very Cute Kitchen with newly upgraded stainless appliances, Open inviting Living room, Shipping container as been converted to Laundry & Storage, Beautiful front Patio Deck, (1) more shipping container at rear of the property will remain for extra storage. Town water supply, Power all on-site. Animal & Pet Friendly.   Gorgeous Arizona desert surrounding this property. The view is so beautiful that it s hard to describe. A real Dream home sitting in the heart of our Mojave Desert. Quietly nestled in at the base of the mountains, in Dolan Springs Lake Mohave ranchos sub-division. You can have all the Privacy, Freedom & Quiet you Desire.    Do you enjoy Boating, Fishing, Hiking, Horseback Riding, Swimming, Quad trail riding, Camping & many more outdoor activities? Endless miles of trails at your backdoor. This is the place for you. Taxes are low and NO HOA to maintain. The weather here is mostly mild all year round and the air is very clean. Enjoy our crisp clear star-studded skies. You will not be disappointed with this simple beautiful Southwest desert retreat. Dolan Springs is just a little over an hour from Las Vegas & airport, 50 minutes to Bullhead City, 50 minutes to Laughlin NV. & 30 minutes to Kingman. With Corridor 11 being built, this is a growing & happening area. Dolan Springs is a High Desert Town with so much history. This home has everything that you could wish for and dream of. THIS HOME WON'T DISAPPOINT YOU.
